name: Hotline Bling Bites
description: A spicy kebab that’ll have you dancing like you’re in a neon-lit cube. You used to call this kebab on your cell phone, late night when you were hungry.

name: Started From the Pita
description: A humble kebab with roots as raw ingredients. Now it's the whole dish, filled with flavors that remind you of your rise to the top.

name: God's Plan Grill
description: A kebab so good, it feels like destiny. Each bite is meticulously planned to give you a divine experience.

name: Views from the Stick
description: A tall skewer loaded with the finest meats, giving you a panoramic taste sensation, reminiscent of the Toronto skyline.

name: Marvin’s Room Munch
description: Perfect for those late-night feelings. A bit salty, a tad spicy, and best enjoyed while reminiscing about past loves.

name: Passionfruit Peppers
description: A tropical twist on the classic kebab, infused with passionfruit and topped with zesty peppers. Perfect for those long-distance food cravings.

name: Nonstop Noms
description: For the kebab lover who just can’t stop. A flavorful marathon that keeps you coming back for more, track after track.

name: OVO-luscious Layers
description: A layered kebab dedicated to October's Very Own. Each layer is a tribute to a different year of his career.

name: Too Good Tandoor
description: This kebab's so good, you'll feel like it's giving you the cold shoulder because you didn't appreciate it enough. Best shared with a duet partner.

name: In My Feelings Flavor
description: Kiki, do you love this kebab? A mix of sweet and spicy that'll have you declaring your love and dancing down the street.
